<br>
Try to pick a point where you've got a good xp rhythm, then pick up the AA's you feel you need, then switch back to normal xp.<br>
<br>
From a psychological perspective, it will seem like you're getting a lot more done that way.<br>
<br>
Others can provide better advice than I on where those points might be in your career.<br>
<br>
